Package org.gridgain.grid.cache

 Start Here  Contains main In-Memory Data Grid APIs.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
GridCache<K,V> Start Here  Main In-Memory Data Grid APIs.
GridCacheConfiguration This interface defines grid cache configuration.
GridCacheEntry<K,V> This interface provides a rich API for working with individual cache entries.
GridCacheMBean This interface defines JMX view on GridCache.
GridCacheMetrics Cache metrics used to obtain statistics on cache itself or any of its entries.
GridCacheProjection<K,V> This interface provides a rich API for working with distributed caches.
GridCacheTx Grid cache transaction.
GridCacheTxSynchronization Synchronization callback for transaction.
 

Class Summary
GridCacheConfigurationAdapter Cache configuration adapter.
 

Enum Summary
GridCacheFlag Cache projection flags that specify projection behaviour.
GridCacheMode Enumeration of all supported caching modes.
GridCachePeekMode Enumeration of all supported cache peek modes.
GridCachePreloadMode Cache preload mode.
GridCacheTxConcurrency Transaction concurrency control.
GridCacheTxIsolation Defines different cache transaction isolation levels.
GridCacheTxState Cache transaction state.
 

Exception Summary
GridCacheFlagException Exception thrown when projection flags check fails.
GridCacheTxHeuristicException Exception thrown whenever grid transaction enters an unknown state.
GridCacheTxOptimisticException Exception thrown whenever grid transactions fail optimistically.
GridCacheTxRollbackException Exception thrown whenever grid transactions has been automatically rolled back.
GridCacheTxTimeoutException Exception thrown whenever grid transactions time out.
 

Annotation Types Summary
GridCacheName Allows to specify cache name from grid computations.
